OL,3,CFirst quarterly fall in average price
OL,4,Cpaid for motor cover in two years
OL,6,FThe average price paid for motor cover
OL,7,Ffell by #13 when comparing the period
OL,8,FApril to June with January to March,
OL,9,Fmarking the first quarterly decrease
OL,10,Fin two years, according to the
OL,11,FAssociation of British Insurers (ABI).
OL,13,FTypical motor insurance premiums fell
OL,14,Fby 2% in April to June this year
OL,15,Fcompared with the first quarter of
OL,16,F2024, taking the average price paid to
OL,17,F#622.
