OL,3,CFirst quarterly fall in average price
OL,4,Cpaid for motor cover in two years
OL,6,FThe drop follows a 1% increase to
OL,7,Fpremiums in the first quarter of this
OL,8,Fyear, when the average premium was
OL,9,F#635.
OL,11,FDespite the quarterly drop in
OL,12,Fpremiums, on an annual basis, average
OL,13,Fpremiums were 21% or around #111
OL,14,Fhigher in the second quarter of this
OL,15,Fyear. In the second quarter of 2023,
OL,16,Fthe average premium was #511.
OL,18,FClaims costs appear to have
OL,19,Fstabilised, the ABI said.
