OL,3,CFirst quarterly fall in average price
OL,4,Cpaid for motor cover in two years
OL,6,FMervyn Skeet, the ABI's director of
OL,7,Fgeneral insurance policy, said: "After
OL,8,Fa very challenging period for insurers
OL,9,Fand customers alike, we're encouraged
OL,10,Fto see an easing of increases to motor
OL,11,Finsurance premiums as claims costs
OL,12,Fstabilise.
OL,14,F"While this is good news, we need to
OL,15,Fcontinue our work focusing on claims
OL,16,Fcosts, for the good of consumers. It
OL,17,Fremains a top priority for us and our
OL,18,Fmember insurers."
