OL,6,FThe ABI's tracker analyses nearly 28
OL,7,Fmillion policies sold a year and is
OL,8,Fbased on prices paid for cover rather
OL,9,Fthan quotes.
OL,11,FRocio Concha, Which? director of
OL,12,Fpolicy and advocacy, said: "It's
OL,13,Fencouraging to see premiums starting
OL,14,Fto fall, and motorists will certainly
OL,15,Fhope this trend continues. However,
OL,16,Fwith premiums rising significantly
OL,17,Fover the past year, many drivers
OL,18,Fopening their renewal quotes will
OL,19,Fstill get a nasty shock.
